Condominiums
Meridian manages a growing portfolio of condominium communities around central Indiana.  Our portfolio includes both older and new communities.  These communities range from ten condominiums to several hundred condominiums.  Our properties include a wide range of communities that having varying prices.  We perform all services needed to manage these condominium communities.  We help our clients develop and maintain reserve accounts, which allow the assets of our clients to be maintained and replaced in a planned fashion instead of in an emergency situation.  We also help provide other day-to-day operation needs as well.  These include collecting fees, paying vendors, reconciling checking accounts, arranging for vendors to provide services trash removal, maintain and improve the existing landscape, remove snow in the winter, and help prepare taxes come tax time.









 










