Specialty
We manage properties for institutions and owners of businesses who want to concentrate more on their core reason of being in business, and would rather not have to worry about maintaining the facility or facilities that they own and occupy.  In these situations, there may be no rent to collect, but there are still roofs, heating and cooling systems, building facades, and landscapes that need to be maintained.  Our portfolio of these types of properties range from office warehouses to a number of bank branches that are located throughout the state.  In this area of work Meridian has also been asked to manage a wide array of foreclosure and receivership properties for lenders and civil courts.  These range from multifamily properties, shopping centers, office buildings, along with a large number of single family homes.









 










