History
Meridian was founded in 1988 by Tom and Gayle Spencer with its headquarters located in Indianapolis, Indiana.  It has grown to become a well respected service company, primarily serving clients with properties in Indiana and surrounding states.  The company started with just a handful of clients and has had a very steady growth pattern since.  Part of what sets Meridian Management apart is its ability to grow, but do so in a responsible manner.  As a company it has always been important to stick with our principles of creating strong relationships with all of our clients.  This is quite evident as Meridian still has some of its original clients from when the company first started.









 










