Welcome to Meridian Management Group!
We provide property management services to the Greater Atlanta metro area. Whether you want to find a new place to live or need a rental filled, when you’re here, you’re home.
At Meridian Management Group, we are focused on your success. For over 15 years, we have been a trusted provider of rental management services throughout the Greater Atlanta metro area. Whether you are new to rental ownership, or you have a sizable and diverse portfolio of rental investments, we can tailor or services to meet your unique management requirements.
Having worked with a variety of owners, investors and renters throughout the years, we understand that every customer is an individual, and that every property requires careful attention to perform well. While we have the resources and experience of a larger firm, we strive to develop strong working relationships with everyone we serve. Once you let us know what your goals are, we will do our best to help you achieve them.
Our firm specializes in the management of multi-family rentals in Atlanta and the surrounding areas. We also offer management services for commercial, retail and single-family properties. If you own one or more rental investments, please contact us now to discuss your management needs.
For renters, you can find information about all available units here on our site. Get in touch if you see something you like – we are standing by to help you find the next home for you or your business.



