Experience




As industry leaders, we specialize in providing comprehensive architectural and engineering services for our telecommunication clients. With over 1,500 successfully completed installations, the professionals at Meridian Management LLC have built a solid reputation for exceeding expectations in design, budget controls, and constructability.
We empower our staff to think freely, to be creative, to always explore more efficient and cost-effective solutions, in an effort to provide the highest quality of service. This explains why we are often called upon to handle the most difficult and challenging sites. We specialize in custom telecom sites of all types, with particular emphasis on complex installations, unapprovable locations, difficult schedules, and innovative technologies. 


