Strategic Alliances


At Meridian Management LLC, we are dedicated to doing what we do best. However, in the ever-changing telecommunications industry, we are always looking for ways to provide our clients with better and more complete service while keeping our core business lean, focused, and competitively priced. To accomplish this, we have developed strategic alliances with a select group of highly qualified firms to compliment our scope of services, increase our resources, and improve our product. Having these strategic alliances allow our clients to leverage the unique capabilities of a team approach without the need and cost of managing this collaboration. 














