FTP




While we do use our proprietary FTP Site for our clients and associates to share drawings, we have found FTP servers a bit difficult to connect with. So we use a popular file sharing service called Box.net.
Box.net is a simple, scalable and affordable solution to manage documents, media and all content online. Share files as a link. Sync files on the desktop. 
To learn more or create an account, go to Box.net
