Our Team






Suzanne Whalen
Chief Executive Officer
 
With over 37 years of specialty insurance and reinsurance management experience in underwriting and product development, Sue leads strategic and key business partner development operations for Meridian.  She began her career in accident and health insurance at AIG and left in 1990 to become President of Hanleigh Management Group, Inc., a special risk MGU. In 1994, Sue and Kevin Leys formed Equinox Management Group, Inc., and acquired certain insurance and reinsurance facilities from Hanleigh; and, in 1999, Equinox spun off all insurance activity into Meridian Management Group, LLC.
 
