The properties and the services you need.
Meridian Management Corporation is a locally owned fee-management company that specializes in managing apartment properties, office buildings condominium communities and homeowners associations, retail center, and corporate facilities.  Meridian Management is full service company that performs a variety of services that include collecting revenue, paying invoices, preparing financial statements and budgets, maintaining the properties, and a number of other tasks that our clients ask us to take care of to satisfy their need.
At Meridian Management we strive to meet all of our clients’ needs.  We believe that through hard work and creating strong relationships with our clients and a variety of vendors that we deal with on a day to day basis we are able to accomplish this goal.









 










